I'd get inpatient on Douglas,
with who was watching

82
00:03:28,521 --> 00:03:30,867
track to track, blood drop, blood drop.

83
00:03:30,868 --> 00:03:34,105
And I'd keep looking ahead, looking ahead,

84
00:03:34,113 --> 00:03:35,563
thinking we'd see something.

85
00:03:35,564 --> 00:03:37,609
But we didn't find him.

86
00:03:37,610 --> 00:03:39,517
- You see the, there's the road,

87
00:03:39,518 --> 00:03:40,348
okay.

88
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:44,106
Yeah it's far out.

89
