and walked across hoping
to kick that kudu out

106
00:04:33,618 --> 00:04:35,948
or at least find sign of it.

107
00:04:38,815 --> 00:04:41,565
(dramatic music)

108
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,139
Down in the valley, we were
just about to go down it,

109
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:49,096
and a kudu ran out, and Leon
shouted, "It's limping."

110
00:04:49,097 --> 00:04:51,847
(dramatic music)

111
00:04:57,711 --> 00:04:59,481
So we hustled over there,
followed these tracks

112
