and heard this huff and there he was,

114
00:05:04,980 --> 00:05:07,760
and seeing him pointing and
I'm trying to get on him,

115
00:05:07,761 --> 00:05:09,585
and he takes off.

116
00:05:09,591 --> 00:05:13,001
Which was good to see him
but discouraging that he

117
00:05:13,002 --> 00:05:16,472
was in such good shape that
he could still run like that.

118
00:05:16,473 --> 00:05:18,245
- You see him, Joe?

119
00:05:18,246 --> 00:05:19,076
- Yeah.

120
00:05:21,496 --> 00:05:22,535
Up in the rocks?

121
00:05:22,536 --> 00:05:25,605
- Yes, on this side of the hill.

122
00:05:25,606 --> 00:05:29,266
- It was trying to, it was
going up another rocky culpie

