00:05:29,269 --> 00:05:33,879
and so we ran ahead of
Geoffrey, and we got to where

124
00:05:33,883 --> 00:05:37,522
we could kinda get a clearing
and we could see him,

125
00:05:37,523 --> 00:05:39,643
he would stop, he'd look
back, and he would keep going.

126
00:05:39,644 --> 00:05:41,749
And he was about half way
up, and I knew if he got

127
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:45,248
over that hill we were back to square one.

128
