- All right.

132
00:05:53,804 --> 00:05:55,826
Leon kinda turned to me and said,

133
00:05:55,832 --> 00:05:59,534
you know, this is gonna be fast, you know

134
00:05:59,535 --> 00:06:02,115
if you got a shot just take it.

135
00:06:03,962 --> 00:06:04,942
- You still see him?

136
00:06:04,942 --> 00:06:05,892
- Yeah.

137
00:06:05,893 --> 00:06:07,465
Right by that bush.

138
00:06:08,838 --> 00:06:11,338
- Take a few deep breaths Joe.

139
00:06:13,122 --> 00:06:15,792
- So we also, actually Leon took the time

140
00:06:15,793 --> 00:06:18,288
to set up his shooting sticks.

141
00:06:19,257 --> 00:06:20,257
Where is he?

142
00:06:21,646 --> 00:06:22,906
- Look up the side of the hill,

143
00:06:22,908 --> 00:06:24,118
just behind that bush.

144
00:06:24,123 --> 00:06:24,961
- Behind.

145
00:06:24,962 --> 00:06:26,366
- Come walking out the left hand side.

146
00:06:26,371 --> 00:06:29,701
Hold a second I'm gonna get you a range.

147
00:06:30,689 --> 00:06:32,878
Joe he's 167 yards.

148
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,219
- I got on it, put it on it.

149
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:37,516
- Deep breaths, gently squeeze the trigger

150
00:06:37,524 --> 00:06:39,944
whenever you're ready.
- Okay.

151
00:06:42,418 --> 00:06:45,418
Shot, whack, and the kudu went down.

152
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:49,610
(gun shots)

153
00:06:49,614 --> 00:06:50,454
- Good shot.

154
00:06:50,455 --> 00:06:51,607
Well done Joe.

155
00:06:53,375 --> 00:06:55,115
- Finally.
