157
00:06:58,594 --> 00:06:59,835
So impressed with you.

158
00:06:59,836 --> 00:07:00,706
Awesome.

159
00:07:00,712 --> 00:07:04,407
- And out was a big sign of relief,

160
00:07:04,408 --> 00:07:07,577
but after what we'd been
through I wasn't gonna

161
00:07:07,578 --> 00:07:10,828
rest until we got up there,
so we hustled right up there

162
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:13,466
and sure enough, behind those bushes,

163
00:07:13,467 --> 00:07:16,507
there was my kudu, finally.

164
00:07:16,511 --> 00:07:19,681
And I was able to put my hands on him.

165
00:07:21,548 --> 00:07:23,068
Make sure.

166
00:07:23,071 --> 00:07:24,111
- Yeah he's done.

167
00:07:24,112 --> 00:07:26,137
Well done.
(laughing)

168
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:27,090
Congratulations.
- Finally.

169
00:07:27,091 --> 00:07:28,468
- Well done sir.
- Finally.

170
00:07:28,471 --> 00:07:30,191
- Make your rifle safe
there if you don't mind.

