00:07:40,334 --> 00:07:42,430
It's right on the shoulder.

175
00:07:42,431 --> 00:07:45,017
If it had just been a little bit back.

176
00:07:45,018 --> 00:07:47,868
- It didn't seem to
slow him down that much.

177
00:07:47,873 --> 00:07:50,022
- No, it did not at all.

178
00:07:50,023 --> 00:07:51,484
He came quite a ways.

179
00:07:51,485 --> 00:07:52,895
- [Joe] How far would you say?

180
00:07:52,902 --> 00:07:54,172
- [Leon] Joe, I think about seven

